@AcidRobot I'm not sure if these changes will be merged in since the `pyFirmata` library really only focuses on communicating with firmata-enabled microcontrollers. The only specific components that are included currently are representations of the [arduino, arduino_mega, arduino_due boards](https://github.com/tino/pyFirmata/blob/master/pyfirmata/__init__.py).

